{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, another topic of interest is whether the impact of green bond issuance on ER shows industry heterogeneity.",
    "The results of sub-sample regression are also important for our research by dividing high-polluting industries and low-polluting industries.",
    "Referring to Pan et al. (2019) and Huang et al. (2022), we select 15 types of heavily polluting industries required by the Ministry of Environmental Protection of China to disclose environmental protection information in 2010.",
    "These include (1) coal mining and washing; (2) oil and gas extraction;",
    "(3) ferrous metal mining and dressing; (4) nonferrous metal mining and dressing;"
  ]
}